description: "This map of Asia is marked with the routes taken through Southeast Asia by the British Royal Navy captain James Cook, and the French explorer Lapérouse. The title also refers to two other explorers: Louis Antoine de Bougainville and William Dampier."
title: "Carte generale de l'Asie : où se trouvent les découvertes faites par Bougainville, Dampier et La Pérouse"
